33:51.000 --> 33:52.240
Xiaolan.

34:06.640 --> 34:07.920
Xia Xiaolan.

34:12.199 --> 34:14.280
N'oublie pas notre promesse.

34:41.239 --> 34:41.840
Zhou Cheng.

34:43.159 --> 34:44.639
